+post-cherry-pick
+~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~~
+
+This hook is invoked by linkgit:git-cherry-pick[1]. This hook is
+called with two parameters. The first is `<old sha1>` and the second
+`<new sha1>`, where `<old sha1>..<new sha1>` describes all new
+cherry-picked commits.
